Hi 
Thank you for getting back to me on your day off! 
I just remember when the tabloids sent their photographer out, they took note of the date on the back which was in 1997 and 
possibly took a picture of it but as I do not want to contact the tabloids right now, I just need the evidence to ensure that is 
correct. If you can, when you get back to the office, is there any chance you could have a look to see if there in fact a date 
mentioned or photographed, it would be very helpful and I would be more than appreciative. 
Have a nice day!! 
On Tuesday. 29 April 2014 12:23 PM. 
Hi 
wrote: 
I'm away from the office today. I don't recall the photo having a date on it but I will review the file when I get a chance.

not to much a bother. Just trying to do get something accomplished! 
Hope all is well!! 
All the best, 
EFTA00030588
